data.description: Click the Virtual Tour link to view the 3D walkthrough. Welcome to this stunning home nestled in a charming neighborhood with clubhouse, pool, and tennis courts. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by beautiful laminate floors. The living room is adorned with soaring ceilings and numerous windows, filling the space in natural light. The living room seamlessly flows into the kitchen, which features an exquisitely large island, complemented by abundant cabinet and counter space. Working from home is a delight in the dedicated home office. The primary bedroom is a retreat unto itself, boasting bay windows and an ensuite bath complete with dual sinks and a luxurious soaking tub. Upstairs you'll find a versatile loft space and 3 additional bedrooms. Outside, the covered patio provides the perfect spot to relax while the fully fenced green space offers both privacy and tranquility. With its modern amenities and convenient location, this home truly embodies comfortable and stylish living!
